658
00:50:08,296 --> 00:50:10,048
Se chama duplo encapamento.

659
00:50:10,590 --> 00:50:13,510
A pena é morte real.

660
00:50:13,593 --> 00:50:16,138
Se mantivermos o cartucho dele,

661
00:50:16,221 --> 00:50:17,931
